           perform   acc-num-doc-000      thru acc-num-doc-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-550.
       acc-ric-sel-650.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
